    <narrative xml:lang="EN">In June 2000, Verdaine made its first investment in acquiring PT Eka Pendawa Sakti (EPS), a 9,100 hectare plantation located in Kabupaten Tapanuli Selatan, North Sumatra Province.  The second investment to be acquired in March 2003 is PT Sahabat Mewah Dan Makmur (SMM), located in Kecamatan Dendang and Gantung, Kabupaten Belitung, in the Province of Bangka  Belitung.  SMM has a 15,000 hectare concession with 8,800 hectare mature area out of 12,000 hectare planted.</narrative>
